{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_28","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc 'cat tasks/prd-vision-support.json'","aggregated_output":"{\n  \"name\": \"Vision Support + REPL/TUI Consolidation\",\n  \"description\": \"Add image input capability across all five providers (openrouter/anthropic/openai/zhipu/llamacpp), introduce crates/image-process for resize/quantize pipeline, consolidate REPL into TUI with TTY auto-detection, and support image input in Telegram/Discord gateway.\",\n  \"branchName\": \"ralph/vision-support\",\n  \"userStories\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-001\",\n      \"title\": \"Config schema — image / vision / context_window 欄位\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want to declare image processing strategy and provider vision capability in config so that the pipeline knows how to process images and which providers support them.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"crates/config/src/schema.rs 新增 ImageConfig struct，包含 strategy: Option<ImageStrategy>（預設 Resize）和 max_dimension: Option<u32>（預設 2048）\",\n        \"ImageStrategy enum 定義 Resize / Quantize / None 三個 variant，serde rename_all = snake_case\",\n        \"Config struct 新增 pub image: ImageConfig，標注 #[serde(default)]\",\n        \"五個 provider config（OpenRouterConfig / AnthropicConfig / OpenAiConfig / ZhipuConfig / LlamaCppConfig）各新增 vision: Option<bool> 和 context_window: Option<usize>\",\n        \"config.example.toml 補上 [image] section 與各 provider 的 vision / context_window 欄位及中文註解\",\n        \"README.zh.md § 設定參考段落同步更新\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"passes\": true,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [],\n      \"completionNotes\": \"Completed by agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-002\",\n      \"title\": \"Domain — ContentBlock::Image variant\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want an Image content block in the LLM domain so that image data can flow through the request pipeline.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"crates/domain/src/llm.rs 的 ContentBlock enum 新增 Image { source: ImageSource } variant\",\n        \"ImageSource struct 包含 media_type: ImageMediaType 與 data: ImageData\",\n        \"ImageMediaType enum 定義 Jpeg / Png / Gif / Webp\",\n        \"ImageData enum 定義 Base64(String) / Url(String)\",\n        \"所有現有 match ContentBlock 的地方補上 Image arm，編譯零 warning\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"passes\": true,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [],\n      \"completionNotes\": \"Completed by agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-003\",\n      \"title\": \"Domain — Message attachments（session 持久化）\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want session messages to carry optional image attachments so that conversation history with images can be persisted and resumed.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"crates/domain/src/message.rs 的 Message struct 新增 attachments: Option<Vec<Attachment>>\",\n        \"Attachment struct 定義 media_type: String 與 data: AttachmentData\",\n        \"AttachmentData enum 定義 Base64(String) / Url(String)\",\n        \"attachments 欄位標注 #[serde(skip_serializing_if = \\\"Option::is_none\\\")]\",\n        \"舊 session JSON（無 attachments 欄位）仍可正常 deserialize，不 panic\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"passes\": true,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [],\n      \"completionNotes\": \"Completed by agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-004\",\n      \"title\": \"crates/image-process — 新 workspace crate\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want a dedicated image-process crate so that image decoding, resizing, and quantization logic is isolated and reusable by both CLI and gateway.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"crates/image-process/ 目錄建立，Cargo.toml 加入 workspace members，依賴：imagequant = \\\"4\\\", png = \\\"0.17\\\", image = { version = \\\"*\\\", features = [\\\"png\\\", \\\"jpeg\\\", \\\"webp\\\", \\\"gif\\\"] }\",\n        \"公開 API：pub fn process(bytes: &[u8], strategy: ImageStrategy, max_dimension: u32) -> Result<ProcessedImage, ImageProcessError>\",\n        \"ProcessedImage struct：pub data: Vec<u8>, pub media_type: &'static str (固定 \\\"image/png\\\"), pub original_size: usize, pub processed_size: usize\",\n        \"ImageStrategy 從 crates/config 引入（use ccode_config::schema::ImageStrategy）\",\n        \"--- Resize pipeline ---\",\n        \"Resize pipeline 步驟 1：image::load_from_memory(bytes) decode 任意格式\",\n        \"Resize pipeline 步驟 2：若 img.width() > max_dimension 或 img.height() > max_dimension，則 img.resize(max_dimension, max_dimension, image::imageops::FilterType::Triangle)（等比縮放，不裁切）\",\n        \"Resize pipeline 步驟 3：let mut buf = Vec::new(); img.write_to(&mut std::io::Cursor::new(&mut buf), image::ImageFormat::Png)?; 回傳 buf\",\n        \"--- Quantize pipeline ---\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 1：先執行 Resize pipeline 縮放（共用同一個 resize 邏輯）\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 2：用 png::Decoder 重新 decode 已 resize 的 PNG bytes，取得 width、height、color_type、bit_depth、buf\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 3：normalize 到 RGBA — match (color_type, bit_depth)：Rgba+Eight → 直接 chunks(4) map 成 imagequant::RGBA；Rgb+Eight → chunks(3) map，a=255；Grayscale+Eight → 每 byte v map 成 r=g=b=v, a=255；GrayscaleAlpha+Eight → chunks(2) map，r=g=b=c[0], a=c[1]；其他格式回傳 ImageProcessError::UnsupportedFormat\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 4：let mut liq = imagequant::new(); liq.set_quality(0, 80)?;（quality 固定 80，不對外暴露）\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 5：let mut image = liq.new_image(&rgba_pixels[..], width, height, 0.0)?; let mut result = liq.quantize(&mut image)?;\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 6：result.set_dithering_level(1.0)?; let (palette, pixels_out) = result.remapped(&mut image)?;\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 7：建立 PNG encoder：png::Encoder::new(writer, width as u32, height as u32)，set_color(png::ColorType::Indexed)，set_depth(png::BitDepth::Eight)，set_compression(png::Compression::Best)\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 8：從 palette 建立 PLTE（每個 color 取 r, g, b）與 tRNS（每個 color 取 a）；只有當 palette 中存在 a != 255 的 color 時才呼叫 encoder.set_trns(trns)，否則不寫 tRNS chunk\",\n        \"Quantize pipeline 步驟 9：encoder.set_palette(plte); let mut writer = encoder.write_header()?; writer.write_image_data(&pixels_out)?; 回傳 PNG bytes\",\n        \"--- None pipeline ---\",\n        \"None pipeline：原始 bytes 原封不動回傳，original_size == processed_size\",\n        \"--- 共用規則 ---\",\n        \"支援輸入格式：PNG / JPEG / WebP / GIF（由 image crate decode）\",\n        \"unit test：對一張 4x4 純色 PNG bytes 跑三種 strategy，驗證輸出均可被 png::Decoder 正確 decode 且 width/height 正確\",\n        \"unit test：對超過 max_dimension 的輸入圖，Resize 與 Quantize strategy 輸出的寬高均 <= max_dimension\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 2,\n      \"passes\": true,\n      \"notes\": \"Quantize pipeline 的核心算法（步驟 2-9）基於 imagequant + png crate 的標準用法，與 TinyPNG 相同原理：palette quantization（256 色）+ Floyd-Steinberg dithering + DEFLATE Best 壓縮。不需要額外參考其他專案。\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [\n        \"US-001\"\n      ],\n      \"completionNotes\": \"Completed by agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-005\",\n      \"title\": \"Ports — ProviderCapabilities + LlmClient::capabilities()\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want the LlmClient trait to expose provider capabilities so that the application layer can guard against sending images to unsupported providers.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"crates/ports/src/provider.rs 新增 ProviderCapabilities { vision: bool, context_window: Option<usize> }\",\n        \"LlmClient trait 新增 fn capabilities(&self) -> ProviderCapabilities\",\n        \"ProviderRouter（crates/provider/src/router.rs）實作 capabilities()，採 conservative merge：任一 provider vision = false 則整體回傳 false\",\n        \"所有現有 adapter（openrouter / anthropic / openai / zhipu / llamacpp）先實作此方法回傳 vision: false, context_window: None（後續 US-006~010 覆寫）\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 2,\n      \"passes\": true,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [\n        \"US-002\"\n      ],\n      \"completionNotes\": \"Completed by agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-006\",\n      \"title\": \"Provider — OpenRouter adapter 視覺支援\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want the OpenRouter adapter to support vision so that images can be sent to OpenRouter vision-capable models.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"OpenRouterAdapter 建構時從 OpenRouterConfig.vision 讀值並存起來\",\n        \"capabilities() 正確回傳 config 宣告的 vision 與 context_window\",\n        \"request 序列化遇到 ContentBlock::Image { Base64 } → { type: \\\"image_url\\\", image_url: { url: \\\"data:<mime>;base64,<data>\\\" } }\",\n        \"request 序列化遇到 ContentBlock::Image { Url } → { type: \\\"image_url\\\", image_url: { url: \\\"<url>\\\" } }\",\n        \"vision = false 時 adapter 行為與現在完全相同\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 3,\n      \"passes\": true,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [\n        \"US-001\",\n        \"US-005\"\n      ],\n      \"completionNotes\": \"Completed by agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-007\",\n      \"title\": \"Provider — Anthropic adapter 視覺支援\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want the Anthropic adapter to support vision using Anthropic's native image format.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"AnthropicAdapter 建構時從 AnthropicConfig.vision 讀值並存起來\",\n        \"capabilities() 正確回傳 config 宣告的 vision 與 context_window\",\n        \"request 序列化遇到 ContentBlock::Image { Base64 } → { type: \\\"image\\\", source: { type: \\\"base64\\\", media_type: \\\"<mime>\\\", data: \\\"<data>\\\" } }\",\n        \"request 序列化遇到 ContentBlock::Image { Url } → 回傳 LlmError::InvalidResponse(\\\"Anthropic does not support image URL source\\\")\",\n        \"vision = false 時 adapter 行為與現在完全相同\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 3,\n      \"passes\": true,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [\n        \"US-001\",\n        \"US-005\"\n      ],\n      \"completionNotes\": \"Completed by agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-008\",\n      \"title\": \"Provider — OpenAI adapter 視覺支援\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want the OpenAI adapter to support vision.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"OpenAiAdapter 建構時從 OpenAiConfig.vision 讀值並存起來\",\n        \"capabilities() 正確回傳 config 宣告的 vision 與 context_window\",\n        \"request 序列化格式與 OpenRouter 相同（image_url，支援 base64 data URL 與直接 URL）\",\n        \"vision = false 時 adapter 行為與現在完全相同\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 3,\n      \"passes\": true,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [\n        \"US-001\",\n        \"US-005\"\n      ],\n      \"completionNotes\": \"Completed by agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-009\",\n      \"title\": \"Provider — Zhipu adapter 視覺支援\",\n      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want the Zhipu adapter to support vision.\",\n   