kspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 6,\n      \"passes\": false,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [\n        \"US-004\",\n        \"US-011\",\n        \"US-012\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-015\",\n      \"title\": \"Gateway — Telegram 圖片接收\",\n      \"description\": \"As a user, I want to send an image to the Telegram bot so that the agent can analyze it.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"telegram.rs / telegram_polling.rs 偵測 message.photo（Telegram 壓縮圖）和 message.document（原始檔案）\",\n        \"呼叫 getFile API 取得 file_path，再以 https://api.telegram.org/file/bot<token>/<file_path> 下載圖片 bytes\",\n        \"下載 bytes 透過 image-process crate 依 gateway 自身 config.image.strategy 處理\",\n        \"agent_bridge::run_agent signature 新增 images: Vec<ImageSource> 參數\",\n        \"provider vision = false 時 bot 回覆「此 provider 不支援圖片輸入」給用戶，不 panic\",\n        \"純文字訊息（無 photo / document）行為完全不變\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings passes\",\n        \"cargo test --workspace passes\"\n      ],\n      \"priority\": 7,\n      \"passes\": false,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"dependsOn\": [\n        \"US-004\",\n        \"US-011\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"US-016\",\n      \"title\": \"Gateway — Discord 圖片接收\",\n      \"description\": \"As a user, I want to attach an image to a Discord slash command so that the agent can analyze it.\",\n      \"acceptanceCriteria\": [\n        \"discord.rs 解析 interaction.data.resolved.attachments，取得 attachment 的 url 與 content_type\",\n        \"以 reqwest 下載 attachment URL 的圖片 bytes\",\n        \"下載 bytes 透過 image-process crate 依 gateway 自身 config.image.strategy 處理\",\n        \"slash command 新增選填的 attachment option（Discord type = ATTACHMENT，option name = image）\",\n        \"provider vision = false 時 Discord interaction 回覆明確錯誤訊息\",\n        \"無 attachment 的純文字指令行為完全不變\",\n        \"cargo fmt --check passes\",\n        \"cargo clippy --workspa